mods.abstract: The recording is of a variety of featured tracks played for the Second Anniversary Program of the WWVA radio station. The recording features a WWVA roll call featuring members of the radio station who were currently deployed during World War Two. The program take bits from October 08, 1944 to December 17, 1944. The programs go in order of: October 16, 1944; October 08, 1944; an unidentified date; October 28, 1944; November 23, 1944; December 17, 1944; December 13, 1944 and an unidentified date.
